snippet.title: Warhammer: Vermintide 2 | Xbox One Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
We're excited to announce that Warhammer: Vermintide 2 releases on Xbox One July 11. 
Play the Open Beta today!
Pre-order now: http://www.vermintide.com/
